CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 26, 1957, pg. 1, reads: "Controversial Lot - William Marks, owner of Mac's Store-to-Door Grocery, is shown driving one of his mobile stores into the controversial parking lot at 2554 Allequippa St. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mac's Store grocery bus with advertisement for Coca Cola pulling in to lot with two other parked buses, 2553 Allequippa Street, Hill District
